data.name: ModificationCommandInvalidEntityState
data.value: Cannot save changes for an entity in state '{entityState}'.

data.name: MultipleProvidersConfigured
data.value: Multiple relational database provider configurations found. A context can only be configured to use a single database provider.

data.name: NamedConnectionStringNotFound
data.value: A named connection string was used, but the name '{name}' was not found in the application's configuration. Note that named connection strings are only supported when using 'IConfiguration' and a service provider, such as in a typical ASP.NET Core application. See https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=850912 for more information.

data.name: NestedAmbientTransactionError
data.value: Root ambient transaction was completed before the nested transaction. The more nested transactions should be completed first.

data.name: NoActiveTransaction
data.value: The connection does not have any active transactions.

data.name: NoConnectionOrConnectionString
data.value: A relational store has been configured without specifying either the DbConnection or connection string to use.

data.name: NoDbCommand
data.value: Cannot create a 'DbCommand' for a non-relational query.

data.name: NoneRelationalTypeMappingOnARelationalTypeMappingSource
data.value: FindMapping on a 'RelationalTypeMappingSource' with a non-relational 'TypeMappingInfo'.

data.name: NonScalarFunctionCannotBeNullable
data.value: Cannot set 'IsNullable' on DbFunction '{functionName}' since the function does not represent a scalar function.

data.name: NonScalarFunctionParameterCannotPropagatesNullability
data.value: Cannot set 'PropagatesNullability' on parameter '{parameterName}' of DbFunction '{functionName}' since function does not represent a scalar function.

data.name: NonTPHTableClash
data.value: Both '{entityType}' and '{otherEntityType}' are mapped to the table '{table}'. All the entity types in a hierarchy that don't have a discriminator must be mapped to different tables. See https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=2130430 for more information.

data.name: NonTPHViewClash
data.value: Both '{entityType}' and '{otherEntityType}' are mapped to the view '{view}'. All the entity types in a hierarchy that don't have a discriminator must be mapped to different views. See https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=2130430 for more information.

data.name: NoProviderConfigured
data.value: No relational database providers are configured. Configure a database provider using 'OnConfiguring' or by creating an ImmutableDbContextOptions with a database provider configured and passing it to the context.

data.name: NullTypeMappingInSqlTree
data.value: Expression '{sqlExpression}' in SQL tree does not have type mapping assigned.

data.name: ParameterNotObjectArray
data.value: Cannot use the value provided for parameter '{parameter}' because it isn't assignable to type object[].

data.name: PendingAmbientTransaction
data.value: This connection was used with an ambient transaction. The original ambient transaction needs to be completed before this connection can be used outside of it.

data.name: ProjectionMappingCountMismatch
data.value: Unable to translate set operation when both sides don't assign values to same properties in the nominal type. Please make sure that the properties are inclued on both sides, consider assigning default value if the property doesn't require a specific value.

data.name: PropertyNotMappedToTable
data.value: The property '{property}' on entity type '{entityType}' is not mapped to the table '{table}'.

data.name: ReadonlyEntitySaved
data.value: The entity type '{entityType}' is not mapped to a table, therefore the entities cannot be persisted to the database. Use 'ToTable' in 'OnModelCreating' to map it.

data.name: RelationalNotInUse
data.value: Relational-specific methods can only be used when the context is using a relational database provider.

data.name: SelectExpressionNonTPHWithCustomTable
data.value: Cannot create 'SelectExpression' with custom 'TableExpressionBase' since result type '{entityType}' is part of hierarchy and does not contain a discriminator property.

data.name: SetOperationsNotAllowedAfterClientEvaluation
data.value: Unable to translate set operation after client projection has been applied. Consider moving the set operation before the last 'Select' call.

data.name: SetOperationsOnDifferentStoreTypes
data.value: Unable to translate set operation when matching columns on both sides have different store types.

data.name: SplitQueryString
data.value: This LINQ query is being executed in split-query mode. The SQL shown is for the first query to be executed. Additional queries may also be executed depending on the results of the first query.

data.name: SqlQueryOverrideMismatch
data.value: The property '{propertySpecification}' has specific configuration for the SQL query '{query}', however it isn't mapped to a column on that query. Remove the specific configuration or map an entity type that contains this property to '{query}'.

data.name: TableNotMappedEntityType
data.value: The entity type '{entityType}' is not mapped to the store object '{table}'.

data.name: TableOverrideMismatch
data.value: The property '{propertySpecification}' has specific configuration for the table '{table}', however it isn't mapped to a column on that table. Remove the specific configuration or map an entity type that contains this property to '{table}'.

data.name: TableValuedFunctionNonTPH
data.value: The element type of result of '{dbFunction}' is mapped to '{entityType}'. This is not supported since '{entityType}' is part of hierarchy and does not contain a discriminator property.

data.name: TimeoutTooBig
data.value: Timeout must be less than or equal to Int32.MaxValue (2147483647) seconds. Provided: {seconds} seconds.

data.name: TimeoutTooSmall
data.value: Timeout must be greater than or equal to zero. Provided: {seconds} seconds.

data.name: TooFewReaderFields
data.value: The underlying reader doesn't have as many fields as expected. Expected: {expected}, actual: {actual}.

data.name: TPHTableMismatch
data.value: '{entityType}' is mapped to the table '{table}' while '{otherEntityType}' is mapped to the table '{otherTable}'. Map all the entity types in the hierarchy to the same table or remove the discriminator and map all of them to different tables. See https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=2130430 for more information.

data.name: TPHViewMismatch
data.value: '{entityType}' is mapped to the view '{view}' while '{otherEntityType}' is mapped to the view '{otherView}'. Map all the entity types in the hierarchy to the same view or remove the discriminator and map all of them to different views. See https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=2130430 for more information.

data.name: TransactionAlreadyStarted
data.value: The connection is already in a transaction and cannot participate in another transaction.

data.name: TransactionAssociatedWithDifferentConnection
data.value: The specified transaction is not associated with the current connection. Only transactions associated with the current connection may be used.

data.name: UnableToBindMemberToEntityProjection
data.value: Unable to bind '{memberType}' '{member}' to entity projection of '{entityType}'.

data.name: UnableToSplitCollectionProjectionInSplitQuery
data.value: The query has been configured to use '{splitQueryEnumValue}' and contains a collection in the 'Select' call, which could not be split into separate query. Please remove '{splitQueryMethodName}' if applied or add '{singleQueryMethodName}' to the query.

data.name: UnhandledExpressionInVisitor
data.value: Unhandled expression '{expression}' of type '{expressionType}' encountered in '{visitor}'.

data.name: UnknownOperation
data.value: The current migration SQL generator '{sqlGeneratorType}' is unable to generate SQL for operations of type '{operationType}'.

data.name: UnsupportedDataOperationStoreType
data.value: The store type '{type}' used for the column '{column}' in a migration data operation is not supported by the current provider.

data.name: UnsupportedOperatorForSqlExpression
data.value: Unsupported operator '{nodeType}' specified for expression of type '{expressionType}'.

data.name: UnsupportedPropertyType
data.value: No mapping to a relational type can be found for property '{entity}.{property}' with the CLR type '{clrType}'.

data.name: UnsupportedStoreType
data.value: The store type '{type}' is not supported by the current provider.

data.name: UnsupportedType
data.value: No mapping to a relational type can be found for the CLR type '{clrType}'.

data.name: UpdateConcurrencyException
data.value: Database operation expected to affect {expectedRows} row(s) but actually affected {actualRows} row(s). Data may have been modified or deleted since entities were loaded. See http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=527962 for information on understanding and handling optimistic concurrency exceptions.

data.name: UpdateDataOperationKeyTypesCountMismatch
data.value: The number of key column types ({typesCount}) doesn't match the number of key columns ({columnsCount}) for the data modification operation on '{table}'. Provide the same number of key column types and key columns.

data.name: UpdateDataOperationKeyValuesCountMismatch
data.value: The number of key values ({valuesCount}) doesn't match the number of key columns ({columnsCount}) for the data modification operation on '{table}'. Provide the same number of key values and key columns.

data.name: UpdateDataOperationNoModel
data.value: The data modification operation on '{table}' is not associated with a model. Either add a model to the migration or specify the column types in all data operations.

data.name: UpdateDataOperationRowCountMismatch
data.value: The number of value rows ({valuesCount}) doesn't match the number of key rows ({keyCount}) for the data modification operation on '{table}'. Provide the same number of value rows and key rows.

data.name: UpdateDataOperationTypesCountMismatch
data.value: The number of column types ({typesCount}) doesn't match the number of columns ({columnsCount}) for the data modification operation on '{table}'. Provide the same number of column types and columns.

data.name: UpdateDataOperationValuesCountMismatch
data.value: The number of values ({valuesCount}) doesn't match the number of columns ({columnsCount}) for the data modification operation on '{table}'. Provide the same number of values and columns.

data.name: UpdateStoreException
data.value: An error occurred while updating the entries. See the inner exception for details.

data.name: ViewOverrideMismatch
data.value: The property '{propertySpecification}' has specific configuration for the view '{table}', however it isn't mapped to a column on that view. Remove the specific configuration or map an entity type that contains this property to '{table}'.

data.name: VisitChildrenMustBeOverridden
data.value: 'VisitChildren' must be overridden in the class deriving from 'SqlExpression'.
